name: Allen County Health
tweet: Mosquitoes are not just a nuisance. They cause more death & disease than any other animal on earth.  But there are a few simple steps to protect yourself and family. Wear insect repellent outside and dump standing water around your home. Find out more:  https://t.co/sCa4iJB0jj  https://t.co/MNhqzgVgdX
